import "./Offers.css" import Greps from "../../Assets/Images/greps.jpg" import Add from "../../Assets/Images/add.png" import Minus from "../../Assets/Images/minus.png" import Raisin from "../../Assets/Images/raisin.avif" import Arrow from "../../Assets/Images/right-arrow.png" import Bar from "../../Assets/Images/bar.avif" import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import React, { useState } from "react"; const Offers = () => { const [quantity, setQuantity] = useState(1); const pricePerUnit = 200; const totalPrice = quantity * pricePerUnit; const handleIncrement = () => { setQuantity((prevQuantity) => prevQuantity + 1); }; const handleDecrement = () => { setQuantity((prevQuantity) => (prevQuantity > 1 ? prevQuantity - 1 : 1)); }; return (

Our Special Offerings

Fresh, Juicy Grapes

Price: {totalPrice}

{quantity}

Natural Raisins

Price: {totalPrice}

{quantity}

Raisin Bars

Price: {totalPrice}

{quantity}
); }; export default Offers
